(173, 16, 'For questions 30-34, please refer to the facts below. <br /> The following is an excerpt from a swap confirmation. The 1-year LIBOR rate applicable to the 6/30/X2 and 6/30/X3 payments equals 4% and 6.25% respectively.  <br /><br />  The swap agreement outlined in this confirmation is most likely an example of:', 'An interest rate swap.', 'A credit default swap.', 'A currency swap.', 'An equity swap.', '', '1', 'Active', NULL),
