(177, 16, 'The market value of the swap agreement increases significantly (in Empire Bank’s favor) during 20X3. Which of the following actions will Vader, Corp. most likely take to ensure compliance with the credit support annex established with Empire Bank?', 'Enter into a separate debt agreement with Empire Bank.', 'Send additional collateral to Empire Bank.', 'Terminate the swap agreement.', 'Deposit additional funds into their margin account.', '', '2', 'Active', NULL),
(178, 16, 'Which of the following combinations would most likely create a synthetic floating rate bond?', 'Company A combines a fixed rate bond with an interest rate swap.', 'Company B combines a floating rate bond with a put option.', 'Company C combines a fixed rate bond with a FX forward.', 'Company D combines a floating rate bond with a credit default swap.', '', '1', 'Active', NULL),
(179, 16, 'For questions 36-38, please refer to the facts below.  The following is an excerpt from a swap confirmation. Settlement amounts are not netted under the terms of this agreement.  <br /><br /> The swap agreement outlined in this confirmation is most likely an example of:', 'An interest rate swap.', 'A credit default swap.', 'A currency swap.', 'An equity swap.', '', '3', 'Active', NULL),
(180, 16, 'The USD and CAD principal amounts included as part of the swap agreement will be:', 'Exchanged on the effective date of the swap only.', 'Exchanged on the maturity date of the swap only.', 'Exchanged on the effective date and the maturity date of the swap.', 'Not be exchanged.', '', '3', 'Active', NULL),
(181, 16, 'Under the terms of this swap agreement, Boba, Inc. will pay $________ to Empire Bank in exchange for $________ on 9/30/X3.', '6.75 million USD; 4.34 million CAD.', '5.40 million CAD; 5.43 million USD.', '5.40 million USD; 5.43 million CAD.', '6.75 million CAD; 4.34 million USD.', '', '4', 'Active', NULL),
(182, 16, 'For questions 39-41, please refer to the facts below.  <br /> Jango, Corp. currently owns a large amount of fixed rate corporate debt issued by Lucas Manufacturing that is denominated in British pounds (GBP). Jango has purchased a credit default swap from Separatist Bank to hedge the credit risk associated with this debt. Jango, Corp. is a public company that files periodic filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission.  <br /><br /> Under the terms of the credit default swap, the reference entity is:', 'Jango, Corp.', 'Lucas Manufacturing.', 'Separatist Bank.', 'The Securities and Exchange Commission.', '', '2', 'Active', NULL),
(183, 16, 'Which of the following events would most likely result in a CDS payment being made by Separatist Bank to Jango, Corp.?', 'The USD/GBP exchange rate decreases.', 'Lucas Manufacturing files for bankruptcy.', 'The overall level of interest rates increases.', 'Jango, Corp. reports a net operating loss in its 10K filing.', '', '2', 'Active', NULL),
(184, 16, 'Dooku, Corp. owns a derivative contract whereby it remits an amount based on the annual return of the S&P 500 in exchange for a fixed rate of interest. This transaction would most likely be classified as:', 'A credit default swap.', 'A commodity swap.', 'An interest rate swap.', 'An equity swap.', '', '4', 'Active', NULL),
(185, 16, 'For questions 42-46, please refer to the facts below. <br />  The following table represents a snapshot of four stock option contracts currently owned by Viceroy Financial. Viceroy did not pay or receive any option premiums for these contracts. <br /><br /> Based on the above information, __________ is/are considered “at-the-money” as of 10/31/X9.', 'Options A & B.', 'Options A & C.', 'Option C only.', 'Option D only.', '', '3', 'Active', NULL),
