(499, 14, '<p><strong>What is the best practice when it comes to setting a policy regarding discrepant invoices?</strong></p>', 'Insist all are resolved before the payment date', 'Let them drag out as long as possible', 'Just short pay and don’t worry about the discrepancies', 'Return the invoice and demand the supplier correct it to your data', '', '1', 'Active', ''),
