(501, 14, '<p><strong>Which of the following is a worst practice when it comes to check signing?</strong></p>', 'Letting Assistant Treasurers become authorized signers', 'Making the controller and authorized signer', 'Using a rubber stamp to sign checks', 'Limiting the number of authorized signers', '', '3', 'Active', ''),
