(506, 14, '<p><strong>What is the best practice when it comes to getting suppliers remittance information related to an electronic payment?</strong></p>', 'Vendors don’t care about remittance information so you needn’t send them any', 'Waiting until they call and then providing it', 'Automatically e-mailing them the information to a prearranged address after every payment', 'Waiting until they e-mail and then providing it', '', '3', 'Active', ''),
