(508, 14, '<p><strong>Which of the following is not a best practice for increasing p-card usage?</strong></p>', 'Only give the cards to employees who ask for one', 'Merge the travel and fuel card into the p-card program', 'Mandate usage', 'Increase the number of merchants in the program', '', '1', 'Active', ''),
